window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>The Greek Gods are dead, but their legacy remains.</b></p> <p>Kairos, pirate lord of Histria, is concerned. A dungeon on his island turns out to be the last entrance to the Underworld, full of wealth and dangers; while beyond the sea the Poison King Mithridates builds up his forces. Enemies old and new prepare for a new war that will determine who shall replace the fallen Olympians. And Kairos is determined to be on the winning side.</p> <p>Don't miss book two of a LitRPG epic loaded with Greek mythology and pirate-themed adventure, from the bestselling author of <i>Vainqueur the Dragon</i> and <i>The Perfect Run</i>.</p>"; 
